Phn loi bnh i tho ng

1. nh ngha vn (Define Problem)

  • M t:

    • B d liu Pima Indians Diabetes bao gm thng tin y t ca ph n thuc b tc da Pima c kh nng mc bnh i tho ng (diabetes) hay khng.
    • D liu c thu thp d on kh nng mc bnh i tho ng da trn cc ch s y sinh.

  • D liu vo:

    • Pregnancies (S ln mang thai)
    • Glucose (Nng glucose huyt tng sau 2 gi trong nghim php dung np glucose)
    • BloodPressure (Huyt p tm trng, mmHg)
    • SkinThickness ( dy np gp da, mm)
    • Insulin (Nng insulin huyt thanh, U/ml)
    • BMI (Ch s khi c th = cn nng/chiu cao, kg/m)
    • DiabetesPedigreeFunction (Ch s nguy c di truyn bnh i tho ng)
    • Age (Tui)

  • Kt qu: Outcome (0 = khng mc bnh i tho ng, 1 = mc bnh i tho ng)

2.Chun b vn (Prepare Problem)

features_only = df_dataset.drop(columns=["Outcome"])

fig, axes = plt.subplots(4, 2, figsize=(14, 12))
axes = axes.flatten()

colors = ["#3498DB", "#E67E22", "#2ECC71", "#9B59B6", 
          "#F1C40F", "#1ABC9C", "#E74C3C", "#95A5A6"]

for i, col in enumerate(features_only.columns):
    box = axes[i].boxplot(
        features_only[col],
        patch_artist=True,          
        flierprops=dict(marker='o', markerfacecolor="black", markersize=5, linestyle="none"),
        medianprops=dict(color="darkred", linewidth=2)
    )
    
    for patch in box['boxes']:
        patch.set_facecolor(colors[i % len(colors)])
    
    axes[i].set_title(f"Boxplot of {col}", fontsize=12)
    axes[i].grid(axis="y", linestyle="--", alpha=0.6)

for j in range(len(features_only.columns), len(axes)):
    fig.delaxes(axes[j])

plt.tight_layout()
plt.show()
